result.name: 嘉寶漢堡 (Kabo Burger)

reviews.text:
Very Bad experience for 1st visiter. 
1. The talk bad to their customers since they leave.
2. No guideline or instruction to show how the shop work for 1st visiters, such as self servicing. 
3. The burger and chips are waiting on the counter since its done, and no one tell the customer is ready and they should grab it by themselves. Then it turn out the food is warm only. 
4. The cashier should go back the school again, he cant finger out the B and P is not the same. When he make a mistake within B and P, and the  Kitchen made it wrong. After that, the customer bring it back for return. The cashier just show “ oh well, what a bad day. You better to take it and go back to your seat, stupid！”
Good Luck if you want to visit next.
Juciy burger with very helpful n friendly staff. Whole experience since walking in the store have been fulfilling
Tasty burgers, the meat tastes so good! I totally recommend

$47 beef cheese burger + mushroom bacon chipotle ketchup. Spicy.

Other types of meat burgers are available too. Adding $15 comes with side snack and drink. Sitting area is pretty small. Diners share big tables. Many people just order takeaway/delivery. English menu is available and each ingredients are written in English too. Unfortunately, credit card is not available.
Good quality burger at a fair price. A bit hot in the summer tho.

reviews.text:
#cassiegotst
-
今日瘦編要去理工大學，去之前經過尖沙咀買左個漢堡飽醫肚！🤣
-
我揀左蜜糖芥茉菠蘿豬堡加烤洋蔥同芝士。佢有勁多汁，好juicy，好易流出黎。菠蘿片好厚好大片，都好多汁。塊豬排都好多肉汁，所以成個飽真係好多汁！😂🐷
-
雖然係貴過M記啲飽超過一倍，但真係物超所值嘅。個蜜糖芥茉汁同豬排個味好夾。👍🏿
-
味道評分▶️🌕🌕🌕🌕🌗 (4.5)
抵食評分▶️️🌕🌕🌕🌗🌑 (3.5)
